From: Kimi Code Review <review@kimi.ai>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 15:59:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Harden workbench-api-updates: security, threading, error handling

This patch addresses critical issues identified in code review:
- Removes hardcoded signing credentials from build.gradle
- Fixes main-thread blocking in ScreenshotAPI, NetworkBindAPI, WallpaperAPI
- Adds null checks for all getSystemService() calls
- Replaces static MediaProjection state with WeakReference to prevent leaks
- Adds missing ProGuard @Keep annotations
- Standardizes exception handling to distinguish SecurityException
- Fixes raw generic types in SocketListener
- Removes commented-out debug code
- Fixes MmsAPI API level check (LOLLIPOP vs LOLLIPOP_MR1)
- Adds proper thread pool management in WallpaperAPI

